11am pst(Right after servers come up)<br>
Meet at Lavastorm Druid Ring<br>
<br>
Anyone Level 46 to 52 is welcome to join the raid.<br>
<br>
NOTHING IS RESERVED!  ALL ITEMS NBG!<br>
<br>
This is not an Eclipsing Synergy raid.. it is open to the membership of the Xev Server.  Whether you are guilded with another guild, looking for a guild, or just want to stay unguilded you are welcome.  If you have thought about joining our guild and would like to see how we doing things, that is ok also.<br>
<br>
Very easy going raid leadership as long as everyone is following instructions properly.  Lets have some fun!<br>
<br>
Some good info to know:<br>
<br>
Please try to bring some resist gear preferably enuff to get to 100 Fire Resist and 100 Magic Resist unbuffed.  Good experienced raid leader and very straight forward.  We would like to keep the raid at MAX 6 Groups and we will be very efficient in our movement thru Sol B.  NBG means NEED BEFORE GREED, that means that only players having the ability to USE an item that may drop as an upgrade to a currently equipped item can be included in the roll for such item.  Epic pieces will be randomed among all those that need the item, level and completeness of quest will not be taken in consideration.  (It is pretty difficult to verify if someone really only needs that ONE piece or if someone hasn't even started their epic 8) )  <br>
<br>
Loot randoms will be held by using the raid leader roll system.  Everyone is not going to do a 1 1000 random for an item.  Tells will be sent to the raid leader and prior to the roll it will be announced those who are interested in an item, and what number is necessary for that person to win the item.  If anyone dies, the random will take place after rezzes are done and tells will be accepted for 2 minutes after announcement of item.<br>
<br>
The raid leader won a Cloak of Flames last week from a dead Naggy, and this is a respectable group of individuals.  Funny loot situations are not going to happen and will never even have a chance to.  <br>
<br>
Classes Desired (Note I said desired not required):<br>
<br>
Clerics 6<br>
Druid 3<br>
Shaman 3<br>
Warrior/Paladin/Shadowknight 6<br>
Ranger/Wizard/Rogue/Necro 6<br>
Enchanter 2<br>
Monk 2<br>
Beastlord/Magician 4<br>
Bard 4<br>
<br>
Please understand that we will take higher level players as priority.  If you would like to reserve your spot please reply to this thread or send Eklipsed a tell in game.  If you have a 65 chanter/druid/cleric/shaman that you would like to bring along to do a buff before we engage you are welcome to.  This is a fun raid.. hope to see many of you there!  It would be nice to see this raid forum a bit more active, lets show Xev that we want to do so.<br>
<br>
If the servers do not come up in time (that NEVER happens.. *grin*) The raid will be cancelled at Noon.<br>
<br>
